{
  "texts": [
    "Extending factuality finetuning to more general prompted generation tasks would be useful.",
    "We initialize all RL finetuning with a model that has already be supervised finetuned to produce responses that consists of an answer or \"I don't know\".",
    "The SFT model we used for initialization is trained predict \"I don't know\" 40% of the time, and to produce the correct answer to the query 60% of the time.",
    "We use a batch size of 32.",
    "We use the AdamW optimizer with learning rate = 1e-5, betas = (0.9, 0.95), eps = 1.0e-8, and weight decay=1.0e-6."
  ]
}